===========

Relation to LSTM
-----------------

| **Single Perceptron**           | **LSTM**                                                                         |
| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| One input → One output          | Processes an entire sequence of inputs.                                          |
| No memory                       | Maintains both short-term and long-term memory.                                  |
| One activation function         | Uses multiple gates (Forget, Input, Output).                                     |
| Suitable for simple predictions | Suitable for language translation, text generation, and time-series forecasting. |


